### M3: Test Token Bypass Could Leak to Production

> **What:** [`auth.middleware.js:49-53`](file:///d:/Mallakhamb-Repo/Mallakhamb-server-refactor/Server/src/middleware/auth.middleware.js#L49-L53) allows `token === 'test-token'` to bypass authentication when `NODE_ENV === 'test'`.
