### L1: Redundant Route Aliases

Multiple routes point to the same controller methods: `/api/superadmin` and `/api/super-admin`, `/dashboard` and `/dashboard/stats`, `/rankings/team` and `/scores/team-rankings`. This adds surface area and testing burden without clear value.

