### L2: DI Container Exported as Module-Level Singleton

[`di-container.js:132`](file:///d:/Mallakhamb-Repo/Mallakhamb-server-refactor/Server/src/infrastructure/di-container.js#L132) exports `new DIContainer()` — a module-level singleton. This makes it harder to test with isolated containers.

**Fix:** Export the class and create the singleton in bootstrap:
```javascript
// di-container.js
module.exports = DIContainer; // export class

// bootstrap.js
const DIContainer = require('./di-container');
const container = new DIContainer();
```

