[`otp.service.js:83-90`](file:///d:/Mallakhamb-Repo/Mallakhamb-server-refactor/Server/src/services/auth/otp.service.js#L83-L90) catches email send errors and logs them, but the OTP is still stored in the database. The user sees a success response but never receives the email.

